info.title: Customer Returns Delivery (A2X)
info.description: This synchronous inbound service enables you to read, create, update, and delete customer returns deliveries. It can be consumed in Fiori apps and on other user interfaces.

x-sap-shortText: Process customer returns with this synchronous inbound service

values.text: [Free of Charge Delivery (BDA)](https://me.sap.com/processnavigator/SolP/BDA " Link To BP ")
[Direct Procurement with Inbound Delivery (2TX)](https://me.sap.com/processnavigator/SolP/2TX " Link To BP ")
[Delivery Processing Without Order Reference (1MI)](https://me.sap.com/processnavigator/SolP/1MI " Link To BP ")

x-sap-extensible.description:
If you are working with key user extensibility, the API can be extended by custom fields on the following business contexts (field usage for this API needs to be selected):
* Shipping: Delivery (LE_SHP_DELIVERY)
* Shipping: Delivery Item (LE_SHP_DELIVERYITEM)

[How to add an extension field to an API](https://help.sap.com/docs/SAP_S4HANA_CLOUD/0f69f8fb28ac4bf48d2b57b9637e81fa/ce819b8557194ae0aa180ba4ac6a04de.html)
